Class EnumerationIterator<E>

    • org.divxdede.collection.EnumerationIterator<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Enumeration<E>

    public class EnumerationIterator<E>
extends Object
implements Enumeration<E>
    Enumeration based on an Iterator or Iterable.
    This class is designed to be used with API that requires the old Enumeration and you need to provide one from an Iterator
    Author:
    André Sébastien (divxdede)
